text: Trichostenidea rufopunctata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae, and the only species in the genus Trichostenidea. It was described by Breuning in 1948.Biolib.cz - Trichostenidea rufopunctata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphorini Category:Beetles described in 1948
